import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App, { Hello } from './App'
import { Travel } from './ooty'
//render("what to show","where to show")
ReactDOM.render(
  <>  
  <App/>
  <Hello/>
  <Travel/>
  
  </>
    ,document.getElementById("root")    
)
